Package com.compendium.meeting

Class Summary
AccessGridData AccessGridData holds the Triplestore and Arena connection data.
Launcher  
MeetingAgendaItem MeetingAgendaItem defines the data object for storing a meeting agenda item.
MeetingAttendee MeetingAttendee defines the data object for storing a meeting attendee.
MeetingDocument MeetingDocument defines the data object for storing a document reference related to a meeting.
MeetingEvent MeetingEvent defines the data object for storing meeting events data.
MeetingItem MeetingItem is the superclass of all loaded Meeting data items.
MeetingManager This class manages a meeting recording session or a meeting replay.
UIMeetingMapDialog Dialog to display meeting data and request creation of the meeting Compendium map.
UIMeetingRecorderDialog Dialog to get the relevant data and create the meeting parent Map.
UIMeetingReplayDialog Dilaog to get the relevant data and connect to the meeting replay.
UIMeetingSetupDialog UIMeetingSetupDialog defines the dialog to enter Arena and Triplstore url and port information
UIMeetingUploadChoiceDialog Displays the options for uploading Meeting data.
UIMeetingUploadDialog Dilaog to present the user with a list of meetings that have been stored to file and can be uploaded.
 

Exception Summary
AccessGridDataException Signals that the AccessGridData required is not complete.
